- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper explores automated tasks and improving performance on various NLP tasks.
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a potential category as the paper discusses deep learning models and their application to NLP tasks.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses augmenting existing networks and improving performance on various tasks.
